  "industry_note": "Polypropylene + 30% glass fiber. Short fiber (1-2mm) vs Long fiber (10-25mm, LGF = better strength). PP-SGF30: σy 60-80 / UTS 70-95 / E 4-6 GPa / ρ 1.10. PP-LGF30 (STAMAX): σy 80-100 / UTS 90-110 / E 6-8 GPa. HDT (1.8 MPa) 150°C (PP unfilled 의 50°C 대비 boost). 가벼움 (PA-GF 의 80% density) + 화학 저항 + 가격 우수 → 자동차 instrument panel carrier, 자동차 battery tray, washing machine drum housing, 가전 외장. Recyclable (vs thermoset GF composite).",
